 <sect1 xml:id="app.s4s.docupdate.2016-02-15">
  <title>February 15, 2016</title>

  <para>
   Updates were made to the following sections. The changes are explained
   below.
  </para>

  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry>
    <term>Updates to the Structure of the Guide
    </term>
    <listitem>
     <para>
      Improve organization of the guide by updating its structure.
      <xref linkend="cha.s4s.plan" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>,
      <xref linkend="cha.s4s.install.sap" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>,
      <citetitle>Configuring &s4s;</citetitle>, and
      <xref linkend="cha.s4s.serve-mediaset" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/> are now
      chapters instead of sections.
     </para>
     <para>
      <xref linkend="app.s4s.component.supplement" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>
      is now an appendix instead of section.
     </para>
     <para>
      <xref linkend="sec.s4s.partition" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>
      is now a section within
      <xref linkend="cha.s4s.plan" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>
      instead of a chapter.
     </para>
     <para>
      Merge <xref linkend="sec.s4s.component" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>
      and <citetitle>Chapter 5, <quote>&sles4sap; Components</quote></citetitle>.
     </para>
     <para>
      Move <xref linkend="sec.s4s.install.network" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>
      from <citetitle>Chapter 3,
      <quote>Remote Installation from a Network Server</quote></citetitle>
      to <xref linkend="cha.s4s.install" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>.
     </para>
     <para>
      Move <xref linkend="sec.s4s.data" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>
      from <xref linkend="cha.s4s.install" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/> to
      <xref linkend="cha.s4s.plan" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>.
     </para>
     <para>
      Move certain information from
      <xref linkend="sec.s4s.component.install" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/> to
      <xref linkend="sec.s4s.workflow-overview" xrefstyle="SectTitleOnPage"/>.
